```diff
+             java.time.Duration.ofSeconds(ConfigReader.getPageLoadTimeout()));
+         getDriver().manage().timeouts().implicitlyWait(
+             java.time.Duration.ofSeconds(ConfigReader.getImplicitWait()));
      }
      
```

</details>
